{"tid":593573,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"你賺左我地幾百萬，叫你老婆比我地玩下，你托手踭? 你係咪唔想撈呀?","createTime":"2018-03-15T06:12:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-18T04:05:19.000Z","uid":133727,"like":5,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"254bb2fccab99aec580850ddd4a228f22e81610d","tid":593573,"uid":133727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T06:12:03.000Z","msg":"勇哥: 「你賺左我地幾百萬，叫你老婆比我地玩下，你托手踭?  你係咪唔想撈呀?」<br />\n<br />\n由呢一句說話開始，我就知道我已經翻唔到轉頭。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我今年三十歲，畢業後入左一間公關公司做，而家既職位名稱係客戶服務主任。<br />\n<br />\n我地公司主要係搞活動，有時動漫節幫人推廣，有時幫啲細公司搞下種樹活動。而我主要係做大project，例如做慈善晚會。<br />\n<br />\n我乜都要做，例如book場，搵mc，邀請社會名流，ceo，高官等等。久而久之，我識左一大班達官貴人，鄉紳父老。佢地係一堆有權有勢，仲大把錢既人。<br />\n<br />\n其中有一個人叫勇哥，佢唔算係達官貴人，佢係一個高官既得力助手，每一次型活動都會見到佢，唔知係咪因為個高官安排既。<br />\n<br />\n有一次機緣巧合之下，我同勇哥認識左，我知道佢搵好多錢，但就收收埋埋，我估都係啲唔見得光既野。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n「老公，我地要一齊努力，盡快買到樓」<br />\n<br />\n講呢個說話既人係我老婆。<br />\n<br />\n我係大學既時候識佢，佢當時好清純，眼大大，水汪汪咁。佢好中意打網球，由於佢身材好好，同埋個樣好清秀，當時好受歡迎。身邊一大堆狗公想埋佢身，但佢就對啲狗公冇興趣。"},{"pid":"8dad4b85b355627a81e22408cff285c18fbf2879","tid":593573,"uid":100117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T07:49:41.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"9924965752d51598d40bf91be190029db2fc393c","tid":593573,"uid":157498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T07:58:08.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"a07d0cea7a375a84125eadba24526266f808916d","tid":593573,"uid":39064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T10:54:27.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"ca7b5d607c8b464135db12e37bb7e02e66cb7826","tid":593573,"uid":166885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T18:41:33.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"82d7bc8ce9840bd9b3575e68869b463461c0fda1","tid":593573,"uid":14541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T00:34:39.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"1751b5a779faa30df745da99ea6c9988f19a5150","tid":593573,"uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T00:35:30.000Z","msg":"樓豬有人回你都唔寫落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35c025a1d09377bf05cd91c57e53a2278e7899a7","tid":593573,"uid":12510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T00:40:59.000Z","msg":"Lm, 加油"},{"pid":"f732bcd8ea7a9767ea17949c2af4d431d9816cfa","tid":593573,"uid":4213,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T00:50:19.000Z","msg":"咁既垃圾文筆就返鄉下啦屌你老母<br />\n識字就出得古咩而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e68aa8aed43d4dc11b7f86100bf9abc7bf2dec1f","tid":593573,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T04:05:19.000Z","msg":"認真睇左一次，又真係幾廢<br />\n咩中意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己讀完唔覺得有鄉音咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有型活動又係乜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋依家嘅職位名稱，好累贅<br />\n索性話 依家已經做到上去乜乜乜咪算"}]}